freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: 10-15 minute period of decreased vision, dizziness and nausea on 1/7/2021 evening. Intermittent nausea and moderate fatigue. Covid-19 swab done 1/8/2021 early morning was negative
Slight nausea and anorexia on 12/26/20 and some continuing anorexia since then. Maybe a bit more fatigue than normal, but may have been due to Christmas holiday activities
Still having intermittent diarrhea, nausea, neck stiffness and headache
